{"tid":2448252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"威廉三子女炮製心意卡向「戴安娜嫲嫲」致意 夏洛特：「爸爸很想念你」","createTime":"2021-03-15T19:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T00:54:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2e17873101c8d8ba18eccf4a6edff159cd073870","tid":2448252,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T19:37:39.000Z","msg":"周日（3月14日）是英國母親節，英國威廉王子三個子女動手製作心意卡向「戴安娜嫲嫲」致意，還寫道「爸爸很想念你」。早前因接受美國名嘴奧花雲費專訪而引起軒然大波的哈里王子，則表示會派人到亡母、已故威爾斯王妃戴安娜的墓地獻花。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210315/CGT5NM7CMRHKLKD4767CZYB3ME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210315%2FCGT5NM7CMRHKLKD4767CZYB3ME%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=0cab1ad5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210315%2FCGT5NM7CMRHKLKD4767CZYB3ME%2F&h=15e7c80d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210315/CGT5NM7CMRHKLKD4767CZYB3ME/</a>"},{"pid":"41abb69e7c74f24b58a9f22adb9145d8766e69b7","tid":2448252,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T00:54:07.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}